{"tid":2121783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［巴膠］有沒有人都鍾意遊巴士河","createTime":"2020-07-23T14:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T14:25:24.000Z","uid":115522,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4e5615e93c437a26f17c9550f4191d2ea575ba16","tid":2121783,"uid":115522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:05:50.000Z","msg":"放假嗰陣 天時暑熱 想出去行吓但又唔想行<br />\n我就會求期揀架巴士上 坐到總站落車 再隨機搭另一架<br />\n一定要坐上層車頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似拍緊公路電影咁<br />\n沿路望住香港 忍唔住感嘆香港真係好靚好多有趣嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n法國咁樣可以去多好多平時唔會去嘅地方 又唔洗熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e69c4ba153450748005259b02d49b151fb5d2c","tid":2121783,"uid":127116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:09:51.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n而家放工時間搭巴士見到個天都好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n望完即刻心情好返哂"},{"pid":"092dd93efa9343a7022ddd384b92618a18e67f59","tid":2121783,"uid":115522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"93e69c4ba153450748005259b02d49b151fb5d2c","tid":2121783,"uid":127116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:09:51.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n而家放工時間搭巴士見到個天都好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n望完即刻心情好返哂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:18:13.000Z","msg":"放工見到晚霞真係覺得香港好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩煩惱都冇哂"},{"pid":"4715b506dee6e9f49142a7c496f880c71275fc9f","tid":2121783,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T14:21:35.000Z","msg":"坐樓下循環線最爽"},{"pid":"4116d356661aad5efdb15314c0e40d5fa19acd20","tid":2121783,"uid":127116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"092dd93efa9343a7022ddd384b92618a18e67f59","tid":2121783,"uid":115522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"93e69c4ba153450748005259b02d49b151fb5d2c","tid":2121783,"uid":127116,"like"